
\section*{Declaration}
\addcontentsline{toc}{section}{Declaration}

This thesis has been created by myself and has not been submitted in any previous application for any degree. The work in this thesis has been undertaken by myself except where otherwise stated. The materials related to region-based skin color technique have been published in \cite{poudel2012}. The work regarding combination of discriminative and descriptive techniques for 3D hand tracking appeared in \cite{poudel2013}.

